- Run "cd ~"
- Make a new folder called "main" and place all the scripts into it
- Place the brainwave readings folder into this folder as well
- Rename the brainwave readings folder to "data"
- Run either "bash auto30sec.sh" (for 30 sec automation) or "bash auto1week.sh" (for 1 week automation)
- If you want to shuffle the data manually, run "bash run.sh" instead